snippet.textDisplay: Thumri (Naina more ... ) and Qawwali (Man Atkeya .... )  are two absolutely different traditions of classical music. The way these two are blended in this  performance is pure magic. The rustic voice of Javed Ji and that velvet touch in that of Akbar Ali are so beautifully used, it gives you goose bumps. The orchestra is so pure and that Guitar masterpiece by late Aamir Zaki in between is a treat to the ears.This is a cult classic and will remain so for time immemorial. God bless.
